{"tid":1960814,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"說好的 AMD YES 呢 !? Steam 3 月報告出爐!! Intel CPU 止跌回升 NVIDIA 升勢強勁","createTime":"2020-04-06T11:25:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T06:28:55.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5f94a53dc60545289f3445a585d0ae4f80c122c2","tid":1960814,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T11:25:52.000Z","msg":"在疫情期間，Steam 遊戲平台屢破同時在線用戶數量，趨勢迎來史無前例的暴漲，日前 Steam 亦公佈了 3 月份的《Steam 硬件及軟件調查》，在 CPU 及 GPU 的統計中，最受玩家歡迎的還是 Intel 及 NVIDIA 的產品，超過 8 成玩家的遊戲平台都是使用 Intel 處理器，一舉收回了近半年間損失的優勢，說好的 AMD Yes 呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？？<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/04/source/06152921611814929377.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F04%2Fsource%2F06152921611814929377.jpg&h=248d9f5b&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/19214/說好的_AMD_YES_Steam_3_月報告出爐_Intel_CPU_止跌回升_NVIDIA_RTX_2060_升勢強勁\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F19214%2F%E8%AA%AA%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84_AMD_YES_Steam_3_%E6%9C%88%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E5%87%BA%E7%88%90_Intel_CPU_%E6%AD%A2%E8%B7%8C%E5%9B%9E%E5%8D%87_NVIDIA_RTX_2060_%E5%8D%87%E5%8B%A2%E5%BC%B7%E5%8B%81&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLTv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=31a2a5d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkepc.com/19214/說好的_AMD_YES_Steam_3_月報告出爐_Intel_CPU_止跌回升_NVIDIA_RTX_2060_升勢強勁</a>"},{"pid":"de553f12cd97aa0ac4cd519981fc31805e5594d2","tid":1960814,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T11:26:55.000Z","msg":"根據 Steam 平台每月給出的《Steam 硬件及軟件調查》，在 2018 年 7 月，AMD 在 PC 處理器的佔有率僅為 15%，到 2020 年2 月份的時候已經上升到了 21.8%，對比 Intel 的佔有率仍有一段差距，不過亦印證了 Zen2 架構處理器上市後 AMD 的市佔在不斷上升的事實。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/04/source/06152023231332452275.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F04%2Fsource%2F06152023231332452275.jpg&h=1b797e1a&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n然而，在 3 月份的數據卻出乎意料之外，Steam 的數據中 AMD 處理器的佔有率由 2 月份的 21.82% 跌到 18.75%，較上月下降 3.07%，而 Intel 處理器的市佔則相應提升，Intel 平台使用率為 81.25%、較上月明顯提升了 3.07%，目前的情況來看，Intel 仍佔據大半江山，看來 AMD 還需更加努力。"},{"pid":"97ad5130d4c38f03b9268dc80b6cec7537eaf129","tid":1960814,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T11:27:50.000Z","msg":"至於 STEAM 玩家 CPU 核心數量的數據（Windows 平台）：截止到 2020 年 3 月份，全平台使用 4 核心 CPU 的玩家依舊佔總人數的一半（佔比 49.66%），但這一數據較上月小幅下跌了 0.08%，目前，6 核心 CPU 的佔有率已達到 24.91%，較上月提升了 3.75%。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/04/source/06155403431232173296.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F04%2Fsource%2F06155403431232173296.jpg&h=90c6c076&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/04/source/0615252020728039352.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F04%2Fsource%2F0615252020728039352.jpg&h=5789a2b4&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"75fd231c705a752c5b797e2b3279c5da1fdbce80","tid":1960814,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T11:28:53.000Z","msg":"除了 CPU 的數據之外，繪圖卡相信仍是大家非常關注的焦點，在 2020 年 3 月的數據中，NVIDIA 的繪圖卡毫無懸念的以 77.87% 的使用率大幅領先 AMD 的 13.38 %。這其中，大家熟知的 GeForce GTX 1060 更佔據了明顯優勢，在全球 Steam 平台中以 16.30% 的使用率遙遙領先排名第二的同門師弟 GeForce GTX 1050Ti（8.62%），該成績較上月提升了 3.62%。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/04/source/06152520201956021497.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F04%2Fsource%2F06152520201956021497.jpg&h=7000b107&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n <br />\n作為一款發佈了 4 年之久的繪圖卡，GTX 1060 繪圖卡仍憑著其準確的市場定位和出色的性價比，為 NVIDIA 提供相當好看的市場數據。緊隨 GTX 1060 的 10 款繪圖卡分別為 GTX 1050Ti、 GTX 1050、GTX 1070、RTX2060、GTX 1080、GTX 1660Ti、GTX 1650、GTX970、GTX 2070，RX580。"},{"pid":"6a2fb0d5e1e20aae17acf59aa6a2c2805e98eaff","tid":1960814,"uid":79829,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T11:28:57.000Z","msg":"intel有口碑<br />\n一般用家冇留意開硬件一定用intel"},{"pid":"9f3d67e9e49fc526d76f81e515a466c0d8010afc","tid":1960814,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T11:29:08.000Z","msg":"增長得最快的繪圖卡則為 RTX 2060，從第 6 位升至第 5 位，相比 2 月環比增加了 0.53%，其他繪圖卡大多集中在 0.1-0.2% 之間。很明顯，RTX 2060 大概率會完美銜接 GTX 1060 成為下一代最受歡迎的遊戲繪圖卡，不得不說 NVIDIA 在產品定義上的實力無人能出其右。<br />\n <br />\n對手 AMD 的繪圖卡在近幾個月的排名中都有提升，3 月份最多玩家選用的是 Radeon RX580，出現在第 11 名，Radeon RX580 在 過去 5 個月以來份額一直在緩慢增長（1.60%-1.95%）。"},{"pid":"185af35c01b49c2e3a53141e8f17debf94ea4efc","tid":1960814,"uid":121058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a2fb0d5e1e20aae17acf59aa6a2c2805e98eaff","tid":1960814,"uid":79829,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T11:28:57.000Z","msg":"intel有口碑<br />\n一般用家冇留意開硬件一定用intel"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T11:30:51.000Z","msg":"GAMER 已經算係核心用家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c4a09c8bdc989ef8a77189bc96acaa7f9e7dfa","tid":1960814,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"185af35c01b49c2e3a53141e8f17debf94ea4efc","tid":1960814,"uid":121058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a2fb0d5e1e20aae17acf59aa6a2c2805e98eaff","tid":1960814,"uid":79829,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T11:28:57.000Z","msg":"intel有口碑<br />\n一般用家冇留意開硬件一定用intel"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T11:30:51.000Z","msg":"GAMER 已經算係核心用家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T11:31:57.000Z","msg":"gamer唔一定留意開硬件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d0bfa66ad88bced750abb5dbc56c7a0f72